[cv_section id="" color_scheme="main" bg_source="default" bg_preset_pattern="green_cup" bg_color="" bg_image="" bg_style="cover" bg_attachment="scroll" bg_video_fallback="" bg_video_webm="" bg_video_ogv="" bg_video_mp4="" bg_scrolling="none" bg_scrolling_speed="normal" overlay_opacity="none" overlay_color="" sidebar_layout="no-sidebar" sidebar="cv_user_sidebar_features-sidebar" parallax="false" min_height="none" stretched="false" border_top="none" border_bottom="none" padding_top="normal" padding_bottom="normal" visibility="all" forced_height="" class=""][cv_row entrance="none" visibility="all"][cv_tab_group orientation="vertical-left"][cv_tab title="Backgrounds" with_icon="false" icon="camera"]

Use A Preset, Or Make Your Own

A quality background is essential for any modern website, and Camyno provides the perfect tool for getting the perfect background. Featuring 25 high quality presets which can be set up with one click and the option to create your own fully customized background the includedbackground editor couldn't be easier to use, and it's included. [cv_image id="1540"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="WooCommerce" with_icon="false" icon="camera"]

WooCommerce Integration

Build an amazing shop that puts all the focus onyour products and encourages your potential (or returning) customers to continue browsing your website, and continue buying your products. Camyno not only supports all of the default WooCommerce functionality but also adds to it withcustom widgets and the ability to further customize your shop. Included is a shortcode that lets you display your products in a list, grid, or carousel format. When using this shortcode you have a choice of two product styles, number of columns, number of products to display and can choose from several options of which products to display. [cv_image id="1088"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Shortcodes" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Dozens Of UniqueShortcodes

Camyno includes more than 40 usefulshortcodesthat work together seamlessly, allowing you to build unique and beautiful pages. Shortcodes can be created using the included visual shortcode composer and added to any page, post, portfolio item, or other custom post type. Shortcodes are also the foundation for the included page builder, and make up the modules you are able to choose from and edit. [cv_image id="1091"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Theme Settings" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Advanced Theme Settings Panel

Camyno includes a powerful theme settings panel that lets you fine tune nearly every aspect of your website using an intuitive interface that won't overwhelm you with a ton of settings. Using the advanced theme settings you are able to easily enable/disable various features in the theme, manage your social media presence, control which share buttons (if any) should be displayed. You are also able to fine tune how your various website favicons should be displayed. Including the standard favicon for most browsers, the metro tile for windows 8 (color & image) and the icon used by most Android & Apple touch devices including tablets and mobile devices. [cv_image id="1084"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="2D/3D LayerSlider" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

User Friendly LayerSlider

Camyno includes the popular LayerSlider WordPress plugin for creating and managing rich and interactive sliders. LayerSlider has been thoroughly integrated into Camyno, your custom sliders can be inserted into pages either directly in their content or as a full width sliderusing the included page builder. [cv_image id="1537"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Camyno Slider" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Powerful Custom Slider

In addition to the powerful LayerSlider plugin Camyno includes its own custom made premium slider. This custom slider can be used to quickly build beautiful sliders with unique captions for each slide composed of any combination of icons, headers, and buttons. Each caption can have 1 of 25 animations to add the perfect touch to your slider transitions. [cv_image id="1092"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Blog Settings" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

8 Unique Blog Variations

Camyno includes 4 different ways to display your blog, coupled with a shortcode/page builder module for easily displaying your posts anywhere means you have total control over your blog. You are also able to display sharing buttons below each post, you even control which share buttons should be enabled. Post formats are also fully supportedwith support for self hosted/3rd party media embedding and unique galleries. [cv_image id="1094"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Custom Widgets" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

5 Custom Widgets

We did everything we could to make your life easier, so Camyno includes 5 custom widgets:Google Maps widget, QR Code widget, Social Media widget, Recent Posts widget, and Recent Portfolio Items widget [cv_image id="1096"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Custom Sidebars" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Create & UseCustom Sidebars

We know how much you like sidebars, so with Camyno you can quickly create and manage unlimitedcustom sidebars right from the widgets page, using a simple sidebar generator which only requires the name of the sidebar you wish to create. Custom sidebars can be used throughout the theme for each page/portfolio item individually and within the page builder. [cv_image id="1097"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Custom Icon Font" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Complete Iconography Control

Icons are one of the best tools available forimproving the readability of a website and establishing bettervisual communication between your website visitors and your website. Camyno incudes a custom icon font featuring hand picked icons from Font Awesome, Fontello, and a few others for the best possible icon font possible. [cv_image id="1098"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Social Media" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Social Media Management Simplified

Included with Camyno is a social media management page with support for more than 15 social media outlets. Each profile you add can be reordered according to priority, links to each outlet can then be displayed in various places throughout the theme individually or as a group.With the social media manager you only need to enterthe URL for each of your profiles once for it to be available throughout the theme, because of this updating your social media is easier than ever, changing a single value updates the entire theme. [cv_image id="1539"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Gravity Forms" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Gravity Forms Integration

Camyno includes its own powerful visual contact form builder, but sometimes you need that little bit of extra control. That's where Gravity Forms comes in, a premium WordPress plugin for building contact forms with an unparalleled level of control and every type of form input imaginable. Gravity Forms has been fully integrated into Camyno, first by adding support for the plugin to the visual color scheme builder and also by adding a page builder module specifically for displaying your forms anywhere. [cv_image id="1538"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Free Support & Updates" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Theme Support & Updates On Us

When you purchase Camyno you are also purchasing your ticket for free lifetime support for your theme as well as free (consistent) updates. Camyno will always be compatible with the latest version of WordPress. Support will be handled through our private dedicated support forums, all you need is your Themeforest purchase code. [cv_image id="1101"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Portfolio Settings" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Create Stunning Portfolios

Camyno ships with a custom portfolio post type and a settings page dedicated to setting your portfolio up exactly how you want. The key to the unparalleled usability of the included portfolio is the integration with the page builder, which lets you display your portfolio items anywhere and in any way. When using the two included shortcodes you are in control over how many columns, how many items, enable/disable pagination & filtering, portfolio item style, and image size. [cv_image id="1106"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Responsive Design" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Touch Screens Love Camyno

Built using the mobile first approach Camyno will work great on any device it is being viewed on. With a fluid grid as the foundation and each content module being independently responsive you can't go wrong. Every aspect of Camyno has been finely tuned to maximize responsiveness. When using the page builder you can even control which content is visible on which sized devices. The responsive menu was custom built to work great on touch screen (or otherwise) devices. Responsiveness can also be fully disabled with a single checkbox. [cv_image id="1115" width="876"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="bbPress Forums" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Build A Thriving Community

bbPress is arguably the most versatile and popular forums plugin available for WordPress, so of course Camyno has full support for it. Use the color scheme builder to customize exactly how your forums should appear, and then use the included page builder modules to display not only your forums, but your forums registration and lost password pages as well. [cv_image id="1103"][/cv_tab][cv_tab title="Events Calendar" with_icon="false" icon="mail-1"]

Schedule & Execute Awesome Events

The Events Calendar plugin is another popular plugin that is supported by Camyno. This plugin allows you to schedule events and display your schedule in various formats for your visitors to browse. This plugin also offers some addonsfor added functionality such as WooCommerce integration. The included color scheme builder supports this plugin so it's easy to customize your events lists. [cv_image id="1104"][/cv_tab][/cv_tab_group][/cv_row][/cv_section]
